{"tid":1682744,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"［擴充業務］黃店開設分店地區建議","createTime":"2019-10-30T08:56:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T11:32:08.000Z","uid":5649,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5a839356832ec38801f1eb71488b41bc71e9e310","tid":1682744,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T08:56:59.000Z","msg":"由於我地已經獲得神獸長龍<br />\n照道理每一區都一定有唔少手足會幫襯黃店<br />\n但奈何唔係區區都有足夠既黃店去懲罰<br />\n我相信有唔少區既巴絲都苦於屋企附近無足夠黃店，唯有幫襯無表態既食店/大快活等資金充裕既大型連鎖食店<br />\n<br />\n以下開放比咁多位巴絲分享所在地區既苦況出黎<br />\n然後利用正負評去提供數據比黃店開設分店<br />\n<br />\n希望咁多位巴絲假以時日可以日日食黃店，建立方便自己既黃色經濟圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275ca371cfbe89ba455efb5b95570b69f09f3fe8","tid":1682744,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T08:57:42.000Z","msg":"認真po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd7f66b956c4a26d54fdac1992303e583d07bcb3","tid":1682744,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"275ca371cfbe89ba455efb5b95570b69f09f3fe8","tid":1682744,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T08:57:42.000Z","msg":"認真po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T08:58:45.000Z","msg":"日日食大快活既我表示受夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想快d有黃店喺屋企附近懲罰"},{"pid":"94165b775e7f7fb1b515295b2f8e3e5d48965115","tid":1682744,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T08:59:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c34193b5cda39c7c62a9604b4a3c18b5e0feba4","tid":1682744,"uid":152061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T08:59:54.000Z","msg":"北區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上水同聯和墟都有幾間出名既，粉嶺南（華明花都果邊）點問都係冇，得一間零食舖又唔可以當飯食，要去上水或者聯和墟已經係要搭車既距離嚟<img src=\